Financial, Inc.\">AX</a></span>), incorporated in 1999 and headquartered in Las Vegas, NV, is a financial services company that primarily offers deposit accounts and mortgage loans through an online banking model.</p> <p>I <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4682446-axos-financial-very-profitable-business-at-attractive-price-ax-stock\">initiated coverage</a> on</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2086436224/image_2086436224.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745750-axos-feds-hawkish-forecast-hits-two-birds-with-one-stone", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 10:50:49", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745757", "title": "Pensions Ramp Coinvestments In 2024 As Sovereign Fund Activity Cools", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Multiply sources of revenue. Multiple streams of income\" data-id=\"1436038027\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"949px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Olivier Le Moal</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Global pension funds feasting on private equity coinvestments are poised to outspend sovereign wealth funds on deals in 2024 for the first time in five years.</p> <p>Aggregate transaction value for pension fund-backed deals, including private equity coinvestments, totaled $65.42</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1436038027/image_1436038027.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745757-pensions-ramp-coinvestments-in-2024-as-sovereign-fund-activity-cools", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 10:45:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745748", "title": "Recent Earnings Disappointment Could Be An Ideal Buying Opportunity For Clover Health", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Close-up Shot of a Doctor\"s Hand Pointing on Brain Scan Images on Digital Tablet' data-id=\"2148728482\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tom Werner</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Healthcare is becoming increasingly big business across the world, as ageing populations demand more and more resources by the year. Nowhere is this more accentuated that the U.S., where the healthcare and insurance landscape means that depending on which side</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148728482/image_2148728482.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745748-recent-earnings-disappointment-could-be-an-ideal-buying-opportunity-for-clover-health", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 10:35:26", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745754", "title": "Joey Politano On The AI Investment Boom And Trends In Economic Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Cloud computing, NFT, AI, artificial intelligence\" data-id=\"1336131137\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1336131137/image_1336131137.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/