outlook for next year and beyond through the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2027091478/image_2027091478.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745749-global-growth-engine-2025-beyond", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 09:40:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745745", "title": "Tutor Perini: Fewer Disputes, More Profits On The Horizon", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tutor Perini headquarters in Sylmar, California, USA.\" data-id=\"1442855367\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Investment thesis</strong></h2> <p>It\u2019s been quite a while since I\u2019ve seen a company tossed and turned by disputes with its customers like Tutor Perini Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TPC\" title=\"Tutor Perini Corporation\">TPC</a></span>) has been for the past few years.</p> <p>In its <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/19906235-tutor-perini-reports-third-quarter-2024-results#hasComeFromMpArticle=false\">third-quarter earnings release</a>, the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1442855367/image_1442855367.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745745-tutor-perini-fewer-disputes-more-profits-on-the-horizon", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 09:25:10", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745742", "title": "Why Veolia's Potential Outweighs Its Risks For Me", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of the Veolia Recycling and Energy Recovery Plant in Leeds\" data-id=\"1435403566\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_1435403566.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1435403566/image_143540